<p>These messages offer a longer-term perspective, focusing on hope, healing, and the enduring power of love.  Acknowledge the pain but gently encourage looking towards the future.</p>
<p>The passing of your mother is a profound loss, but her love and influence will forever remain. May the strength of your memories sustain you through this challenging journey.  Take your time to grieve, and remember that healing takes time.  Let the love and support of family and friends be your guiding light during this difficult time.</p>
